message.body: Hey Jeremy.....my name is Matt. I play in a band with Ricardo, and I left some stuff at the space. I don't have keys and ricardo's not around for the nex
t few days. Will you be at the space at all tomorrow by any chance? If so, could I swing by then to grab my stuff?
I will be there a bunch on Sunday, would that work?
Hey man, thanks for getting back. I'm leaving Sunday morning. How early are you getting there on Sunday?
Was plannin on goin over at 2, but I could meet ya earlier
I think I gotta head out around 10. Could I swing by your place to grab keys and then bring them right back?
I know the deal with the alarm deactivation and reactivation
Ok sweet. I'll text you before I'm about to head over Sunday morning
